# clang-tidy ≥ 22 errors out with "no checks enabled" unless a check set is
# configured explicitly. This restores the historical default set
# (clang-diagnostic-* + clang-analyzer-*). The DeprecatedOrUnsafeBufferHandling
# checker is excluded: it bans memcpy/memset wholesale in favor of the C11
# Annex K *_s functions, which our embedded libc does not provide.
Checks: >
  clang-diagnostic-*,
  clang-analyzer-*,
  -clang-analyzer-security.insecureAPI.DeprecatedOrUnsafeBufferHandling
